{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"CSSNumericValue","mdn_url":"/pl/docs/Web/API/CSSNumericValue","locale":"pl","native":"Polski","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/CSSNumericValue\"><code>CSSNumericValue</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Metody</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSNumericValue/add\"><code>add()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/CSSNumericValue/div\"><code>div()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSNumericValue/equals\"><code>equals()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSNumericValue/max\"><code>max()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSNumericValue/min\"><code>min()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSNumericValue/mul\"><code>mul()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSNumericValue/parse\"><code>parse()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSNumericValue/sub\"><code>sub()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSNumericValue/to\"><code>to()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSNumericValue/toSum\"><code>toSum()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSNumericValue/type\"><code>type()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Inheritance:</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleValue\"><code>CSSStyleValue</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"><div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect2\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>This is an <a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Guidelines/Conventions_definitions#experimental\">experimental technology</a></strong><br>Check the <a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">Browser compatibility table</a> carefully before using this in production.</p></div></div>\n\n<p class=\"summary\">The <strong><code>CSSNumericValue</code></strong> interface of the <a href=\"/docs/Web/API/CSS_Typed_Object_Model_API\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">CSS Typed Object Model API</a> represents operations that all numeric values can perform.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"interfaces_based_on_cssnumericvalue","title":"Interfaces based on CSSNumericValue","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Below is a list of interfaces based on the CSSNumericValue interface.</p>\n\n<div class=\"index\" id=\"sect3\">\n<ul>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSMathInvert\"><code>CSSMathInvert</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSMathMax\"><code>CSSMathMax</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSMathMin\"><code>CSSMathMin</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSMathNegate\"><code>CSSMathNegate</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSMathProduct\"><code>CSSMathProduct</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSMathSum\"><code>CSSMathSum</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSMathValue\"><code>CSSMathValue</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSNumericArray\"><code>CSSNumericArray</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSPerspective\"><code>CSSPerspective</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSPositionValue\"><code>CSSPositionValue</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSRotate\"><code>CSSRotate</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSSkew\"><code>CSSSkew</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"The documentation about this has not yet been written; please consider contributing!\"><code>CSSSkeyX</code></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"The documentation about this has not yet been written; please consider contributing!\"><code>CSSSkeyW</code></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSTranslate\"><code>CSSTranslate</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSUnitValue\"><code>CSSUnitValue</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"properties","title":"Properties","isH3":false,"content":"<p>None.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"event_handlers","title":"Event handlers","isH3":true,"content":"<p>No</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"methods","title":"Methods","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"cssnumericvalue.add_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSNumericValue/add\"><code>CSSNumericValue.add</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Adds a supplied number to the <code>CSSNumericValue</code>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"cssnumericvalue.sub_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSNumericValue/sub\"><code>CSSNumericValue.sub</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Subtracts a supplied number from the <code>CSSNumericValue</code>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"cssnumericvalue.mul_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSNumericValue/mul\"><code>CSSNumericValue.mul</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Multiplies the <code>CSSNumericValue</code> by the supplied value.</dd>\n <dt id=\"cssnumericvalue.div\"><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/CSSNumericValue/div\"><code>CSSNumericValue.div</code></a></dt>\n <dd>Divides the <code>CSSNumericValue</code> by the supplied value.</dd>\n <dt id=\"cssnumericvalue.min_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSNumericValue/min\"><code>CSSNumericValue.min</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Returns the minimum value passed</dd>\n <dt id=\"cssnumericvalue.max_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSNumericValue/max\"><code>CSSNumericValue.max</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Returns the maximum value passed</dd>\n <dt id=\"cssnumericvalue.equals_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSNumericValue/equals\"><code>CSSNumericValue.equals</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd><em>True</em> if all the values are the exact same type and value, in the same order. Otherwise, <em>false.</em></dd>\n <dt id=\"cssnumericvalue.to_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSNumericValue/to\"><code>CSSNumericValue.to</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Converts <code>value</code> into another one with the specified <var>unit.</var></dd>\n <dt id=\"cssnumericvalue.tosum_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSNumericValue/toSum\"><code>CSSNumericValue.toSum</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>TBD</dd>\n <dt id=\"cssnumericvalue.type_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSNumericValue/type\"><code>CSSNumericValue.type</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>TBD</dd>\n <dt id=\"cssnumericvalue.parse_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSNumericValue/parse\"><code>CSSNumericValue.parse</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Allows a <code class=\"idl\">CSSNumericValue</code> to be constructed directly from a string containing CSS.&nbsp;</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"Specifications","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://drafts.css-houdini.org/css-typed-om-1/#numeric-value\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">CSS Typed OM Level 1<br><small lang=\"pl\">The definition of 'CSSNumericValue' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">Working Draft</span></td>\n   <td>Initial definition.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.CSSNumericValue","dataURL":"/pl/docs/Web/API/CSSNumericValue/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See Also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSImageValue\"><code>CSSImageValue</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSKeywordValue\"><code>CSSKeywordValue</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSPositionValue\"><code>CSSPositionValue</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSTransformValue\"><code>CSSTransformValue</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSUnparsedValue\"><code>CSSUnparsedValue</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Interfaces based on CSSNumericValue","id":"interfaces_based_on_cssnumericvalue"},{"text":"Properties","id":"properties"},{"text":"Methods","id":"methods"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"See Also","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"The CSSNumericValue interface of the CSS Typed Object Model API represents operations that all numeric values can perform.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_tra